  "text": "Individual disruption of the RPL12A and RPL12B genes has shown that their respective contribution to the cell ScL12 protein content is not identical [CITATION_1] . Thus, deletion of RPL12B results in a larger reduction of the growth rate and ScL12 content than deletion of RPL12A, however, the differences were not big (36).",
